---+ Post Upgrade Functionality Checks

This document is to provide a list of checks that will test the functionality of the Display service after an upgrade has been done.

---++ Checks Immediately after service is brought up
   * Login to display.grid.iu.edu and become root
      * Execute /opt/service-monitor/display/test.sh Any errors will generate an alert e-mail.
   * Verify [[http://display.grid.iu.edu/][display]] is up. Page should load in a reasonable amount of time and have expected content.
   * Observe the web page, it should automatically cycle between views with a period of about a minute.

---++ Checks 15 minutes after service is brought up
   * Verify the time stamp (near the bottom) is current.

